title: Benny the Butcher interview
itunes:title: Benny the Butcher interview
description:
Today onthe show we had our guy Benny the Butcher stop by where he spoke lyrical content, Griselda Roots, Roc Nation, respecting your peers and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to the Michigan governor, after he said rape victims shouldn’t abort because “they were put in the moment by god and that baby could be the next president”. Also, Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee" where one listener needed help getting out of an abusive relationship.
